Masana ilimin geophysics sun lura cewa bayan girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.1 a tsakiyar Mexico a watan Satumbar 2017, wani dutse mai fitad da wuta da ke da nisan mil 45 (72 km) daga babban birnin kasar ya fara aiki.
