An yi arangama tsakanin ' yan sanda da ' yan gurguzu a Catalonia a ranar tunawa da zaben raba gardama
An kama mutane shida a ranar Asabar bayan rikici tsakanin masu zanga-zangar neman 'yancin kai da jami'an 'yan sanda a Barcelona, inda dubban mutane suka yi zanga-zanga don tunawa da ranar farko ta raba gardamar raba yankin Catalonia.
Da zarar 'yan sanda suka fara janye masu zanga-zangar masu rufe fuska, sai suka jefa wa' yan sanda kwai, suka yayyafa musu tawada, kuma suka rufe titunan da ke cike da masu yawon bude ido da hazo.
Daga baya a wannan ranar, an yi gwagwarmaya tsakanin 'yan sanda da' yan sanda da suka yi amfani da makamai don kashe rikici.
Ƙungiyoyin 'yancin kai da suka yi ta rera taken "Ba za mu manta ba, ba za mu gafarta ba" na tsawon sa'o'i da yawa sun fuskanci masu zanga-zangar ƙungiyoyin kwadago da ke ihu "Spain ta daɗe".
Kafofin watsa labarai na kasar sun ruwaito cewa an ba da taimakon likita ga mutane 14 da suka ji rauni a lokacin zanga-zangar.
Duk da cewa an yi shekara guda da zaben raba gardama a ranar 1 ga watan Oktoba, wanda Madrid ta bayyana ba bisa doka ba, kuma 'yan gurguzu na Catalonia sun yi bikin nasarar, har yanzu akwai tashin hankali a yankin da aka ayyana' yancin kai.
Masu jefa kuri'a sun samu rinjaye mai yawa don 'yancin kai, amma ba su da yawa saboda kusan duk waɗanda suka ƙi raba sun yi watsi da zaben.
Gwamnatin Catalonia ta ce a shekarar da ta gabata, an yi rikici da 'yan sanda a wuraren da ake gudanar da zabe, inda mutane kusan 1,000 suka ji rauni.
Kungiyoyin masu goyon bayan 'yancin kai sun kwana a filin a ranar Juma'a don hana zanga-zangar nuna goyon baya ga 'yan sanda na jihar.
Ko da yake akwai wani abu da ya faru, amma kamar dai an tilasta masa ya koma wani wuri.
Wani mai aikin lantarki mai shekaru 68 mai suna Narkiz Termez ya halarci zanga-zangar 'yan tawaye tare da matarsa, wanda ya ce: "Na rasa bege na karshe na Catalonia don samun 'yancin kai".
A shekarar da ta gabata mun yi rayuwa mai kyau.
Iyayena, waɗanda suka sami damar yin zabe, sun yi kuka, amma yanzu sun fi ƙarfin hali", in ji ta.
Duk da cewa sun samu nasara a zaben yanki da aka yi tsammani a watan Disambar bara, jam'iyyun 'yancin kai na Catalonia sun ci gaba da yin ƙoƙari a wannan shekara, saboda manyan shugabannin da aka kora ko kuma aka tsare a kurkuku don ayyukansu na yin shelar 'yancin kai.
Joan Puig, mai aikin injiniya mai shekaru 42, ya dauki bidiyon wannan zanga-zangar a wayar sa don nuna goyon baya ga 'yan sanda, 'yan siyasa daga bangarorin biyu da ke kara tayar da hankali.
Ya ce, "Yanayin yana taɓarɓarewa".
Wani daga cikin shugabannin Catalonia tara da ke jiran hukunci tun a shekarar da ta gabata, Oriol Junqueras, ya ce zai tsaya takarar zaben majalisar Turai a ranar Asabar.
"Tsowa takarar zaben Turai ita ce hanya mafi kyau da za ta fallasa lalacewar dabi'un dimokiradiyya da kuma matsin lamba daga gwamnatin Spain", in ji ta.
