Livingston ya jagoranci Rangers zuwa ga nasara ta biyu a wasanni 18 bayan da aka nada shi manajan kungiyar ta Steven Gerrard Ibrox, wanda ya tashi zuwa mataki na farko a gasar.
Dolly Minga ta yi fice a wasan da ta buga, domin ta yi nasara wajen daidaitawa da Hibernian, tawagar Gary Holt.
Gerrard ya kasa cin nasara a wasan waje a gasar Premier a wannan kakar, inda ya ci gaba da kasancewa a baya da maki takwas a ranar Lahadi da ta gabata.
A ranar Alhamis, Rangers ta karbi Rapid na Vienna a filin wasa na Europa League.
A halin yanzu, Livingston ya ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin wasanni shida na gasar, kuma ya sha wahala daga rashin nasara a hannun Holt, wanda ya maye gurbin Kenny Miller a watan jiya.
Livingston ya yi amfani da damarsa a gaban masu sauraro
Holt ya gaji da Rangers a wasan da ya yi, kuma ya ci gaba da ci gaba kafin ya ci gaba da zira kwallaye.
Scott Robinson ya ci gaba da tsalle, amma ya fuskanci rikici a lokacin da yake zuwa, sannan Alan Lithgow ya yi ƙoƙari ya buga Craig Halkett a raga.
