Rangers sun rasa bugun fanfo, kuma lokacin da Livingston ya kai ga zura kwallo, Declan Gallagher da Robinson sun kusanci Minga, wanda ya dauki kwallon kuma ya zira kwallo daga tsakiyar filin.
A wannan lokacin Rangers sun ci gaba da cin nasara, amma ba su iya tsallake kariya mai karfi ba kuma ba su da wata barazana ga mai tsaron gida Liam Kelly.
Ko da yake wannan yanayin ya ci gaba har zuwa rabi na biyu, Alfredo Morelos ya ɗauki bugun da Kelly ya yi.
Scott Pittman ya buga wa mai tsaron gidan Rangers Allan McGregor a kafa, kuma Lithgow ya sake dawowa a cikin hanyar Livingston.
An sake buga wasannin da aka yi a filin wasa na Livingston, amma an yi amfani da shi sau biyu don cin nasara, daya don Halkett Glenn Middleton ya yi tsayayya da shi, kuma daya don buga kwallon.
