Har ila yau, Rangers ba su iya yin kome ba game da harbi mai zurfi na Jacobs.
Scott Arfield bai yi wani abu ba, saboda Declan Gallagher ya ba da kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya yi ƙoƙari ya tura shi zuwa Minga don kammala wasan.
