Bikin na Global Citizen wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012 ya ci gaba da aikin Global Poverty Project, kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta duniya, wanda ke neman kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan masu aiki a yaki da talauci.
