"Dole ne mu yi kwangila", in ji Mr. Clark.
Wani kamfanin kera motoci na kasar Japan ya ce jinkirin da aka samu a kan iyakar kasar sakamakon rashin aiki na Brexit zai iya haifar da raguwar ayyukan yi.
Kamfanin Burnaston, wanda ke kera motocin Toyota Auris da Avensis, ya samar da motoci kusan 150,000,000 a bara, kuma an fitar da kashi 90% zuwa sauran sassan Tarayyar Turai.
"Ina tsammanin idan Birtaniya ta bar Tarayyar Turai a karshen watan Maris, za mu ga cewa masana'antunmu sun daina aiki", in ji Marvin Cook, shugaban kamfanin Toyota a yankin Burnaston.
Wasu manyan kamfanonin kera motoci na Burtaniya kamar Honda, BMW da Jaguar Land Rover sun nuna damuwarsu game da ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai ba tare da yarjejeniyar kasuwanci ta kan iyaka ba.
