Za a iya jinkirta ganawar Donald Trump da mataimakin Babban Lauyan Rod Rosenstein "har zuwa mako guda" yayin da Brett Kavanaugh ke ci gaba da fafatawa don zama a Kotun Koli, Fadar White House ta fada a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein ya lura da aikin Robert Mueller, mai ba da shawara na musamman, wanda ke kula da al'amuran da suka shafi tsoma baki na Rasha a zaben, hulɗa tsakanin Trump da masu ba da shawara na Rasha, da kuma yiwuwar hana shugaban kasa yin adalci.
