Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesiya
A ranar Juma'a, girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka afku a birnin Palo a kasar Indonesia sun kashe mutane 384 kuma jami'ai sun ce ana sa ran adadin zai karu.
Saboda katsewar sadarwa, ma'aikatan cibiyoyin agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala da ke arewacin garin Palu ba, kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga Palau bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi kuma yana kan gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, a ƙarshen tashar jirgin ruwa mai faɗi, yana da mazaunan kusan 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da haihuwarsa.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi wanda ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mi).
Gundumar da ke cikin ƙananan lardin ta kasance mai yawan jama'a 299,200 a shekara ta 2017.
Kifi da aikin gona sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Har ila yau, hakar nickel yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma yawancin masana'antu suna cikin Morawa, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Indonesia ta ce a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya kai wa ga Palau da Donggala a kai a kai.
Tsunami da ya auku a shekara ta 1938 ya halaka mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami da ya auku a yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996 ya kashe mutane tara.
Domin ƙasar Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa, wato, "Ring of Fire of the Pacific", ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a cikin ' yan shekarun nan sune:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a yammacin gabar lardin Aceh da ke arewacin tsibirin Sumatra a Indonesia a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami a kasashe 14, sakamakon mutuwar mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabi a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, an yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin tsibirin Sumatra.
A tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra, mutane da yawa sun mutu.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 6.8 ta afku a tsibirin Java, mafi yawan jama'a a kudancin Indonesia, ta kai ga gabar kudu, ta kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.6 ta auku a birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 sun mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 a tsibirin Metawai a Sumatra ta haifar da tsunami mai zurfin mita 10, wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: A cikin jihar Pidie-Jai a Aceh, an yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarancin ruwa, wanda ya haifar da bala'i da firgici a cikin jama'a, saboda an yi gargadin mutane game da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na shekarar 2004.
Amma ba a yi tsunami ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a ƙarƙashin gine-ginen da suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin yawon shakatawa na Lombok a Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500 a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta hana dubban masu yawon bude ido komawa gidajensu na ɗan lokaci.
